# Create full structure
mkdir -p .claude/skills/{bond-data-profiler,data-availability-checker,carry-backtest,research-workflow}
mkdir -p .claude/commands
mkdir -p docs reports

# Start Claude and create files
claude

> Create the CLAUDE.md file with project conventions for a credit trading research platform.
> Include: code standards, data conventions, key paths, available skills, anti-patterns.

> Create the bond-data-profiler skill at .claude/skills/bond-data-profiler/

> Create the data-availability-checker skill at .claude/skills/data-availability-checker/

> Create the carry-backtest skill at .claude/skills/carry-backtest/

> Create the research-workflow skill at .claude/skills/research-workflow/

> Create slash commands in .claude/commands/ for profile-data, check-data, run-backtest

# Commit
git add CLAUDE.md .claude/ docs/
git commit -m "Add Claude Code configuration: skills, commands, conventions"
```

---

## Workflow Integration
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        CLAUDE.md                                │
│              (always loaded: style, paths, rules)               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                              │
           ┌──────────────────┼──────────────────┐
           ▼                  ▼                  ▼
   ┌───────────────┐  ┌───────────────┐  ┌───────────────┐
   │ bond-data-    │  │ data-avail-   │  │ carry-        │
   │ profiler      │  │ ability-      │  │ backtest      │
   │               │  │ checker       │  │               │
   │ "Profile the  │  │ "Can I run a  │  │ "Run carry    │
   │  TRACE data"  │  │  2Y backtest  │  │  backtest"    │
   │               │  │  on IG 5-7Y?" │  │               │
   └───────────────┘  └───────────────┘  └───────────────┘
           │                  │                  │
           ▼                  ▼                  ▼
   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │                    reports/                         │
   │  - dataset_summary.md                               │
   │  - data_availability_YYYYMMDD.md                    │
   │  - backtest_carry_YYYYMMDD.md                       │
   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
